name: [ Casa ] Special Edition
description: Old places - Live places | [ Casa ] Special Edition - is a 3D recording of an old construction located in the heart of downtown Oaxaca, a place that has witnessed time and breathes new memories every time someone walks through it, such a natural experience between time, space and humans. Part of the series Memorias Orgánicas a work of exploration and registration through 3D scanning on endemic natural elements of Oaxaca, México. | 1920 x 1080 px | http://f3.studio/ | IG: @f3.output TW: @F3_STUDI0
